And then we'll do a brief overview

43:49.800 --> 43:52.960
at the conclusion of the item on the legislative action

43:52.960 --> 43:55.840
that has taken place since we last met

43:56.680 --> 43:57.920
for the California School Dashboard

43:57.920 --> 44:00.280
