So to get us started,

44:04.040 --> 44:09.040
the recommendation is that the Department of Education

44:10.000 --> 44:11.520
is asking the State Board of Education

44:11.520 --> 44:13.080
to provide guidance as appropriate

44:13.080 --> 44:16.560
on proposed student growth model methodology.

