so that we can provide results to the field

45:03.320 --> 45:06.760
based on past information, prior students,

45:06.760 --> 45:09.200
on how they're doing and get the field comfortable

45:09.200 --> 45:11.320
and our parents and community members comfortable

45:11.320 --> 45:13.440
